com.shouldis.bitset.parallel.Biterator

Packages that use Biterator 
Package Description
com.shouldis.bitset.parallel  

  • Uses of Biterator in com.shouldis.bitset.parallel

    Subclasses of Biterator in com.shouldis.bitset.parallel 
    Modifier and Type Class Description
    class  ArrayBiterator
    Implementation of SizedBiterator used to stream all values within a specified integer array representing indices in an order appropriate to manipulate a BitSet in parallel.
    class  CompoundBiterator
    Implementation of Biterator that creates a stream of indices that represents which bits will be live after performing a CompoundBiterator.bitwiseFunction(long, long) between the words of 2 BitSets at the same word index.
    static class  CompoundBiterator.And
    Implementation of CompoundBiterator used to stream the indices of bits that result in the live state after the AND operation, splitting at appropriate indices to manipulate a BitSet in parallel.
    static class  CompoundBiterator.NotAnd
    Implementation of CompoundBiterator used to stream the indices of bits that result in the dead state after the AND operation, splitting at appropriate indices to manipulate a BitSet in parallel.
    static class  CompoundBiterator.NotOr
    Implementation of CompoundBiterator used to stream the indices of bits that result in the dead state after the OR operation, splitting at appropriate indices to manipulate a BitSet in parallel.
    static class  CompoundBiterator.NotXOr
    Implementation of CompoundBiterator used to stream the indices of bits that result in the dead state after the XOR operation, splitting at appropriate indices to manipulate a BitSet in parallel.
    static class  CompoundBiterator.Or
    Implementation of CompoundBiterator used to stream the indices of bits that result in the live state after the OR operation, splitting at appropriate indices to manipulate a BitSet in parallel.
    static class  CompoundBiterator.XOr
    Implementation of CompoundBiterator used to stream the indices of bits that result in the live state after the XOR operation, splitting at appropriate indices to manipulate a BitSet in parallel.
    class  DeadBiterator
    Implementation of Biterator used to stream the indices of dead bits within a BitSet, splitting at appropriate indices to manipulate a BitSet in parallel.
    class  LiveBiterator
    Implementation of Biterator used to stream the indices of live bits within a BitSet, splitting at appropriate indices to manipulate a BitSet in parallel.
    class  RangeBiterator
    Implementation of SizedBiterator used to stream all indices of a specified range, splitting at appropriate indices to manipulate a BitSet in parallel.
    class  SizedBiterator
    Implementation of Biterator that is meant to be used when streaming a known number of indices.
